.. _-D:

**-D**\ [**j**\|\ **J**]\ *dx*\ [/*dy*][**+v**\ [*pen*]]
    Offset the text from the projected (*x*,\ *y*) point by *dx*,\ *dy*
    [0/0]. If *dy* is not specified then it is set equal to *dx*. Use
